(7, 1, 'World\'s animal population has declined 60% since 1970 — and experts fear trend will continue', 'A decade-long study of the loggerhead turtle showed 35% of the analyzed species had ingested debris — nearly all which was plastic. (hocus-focus / Getty Images)', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">The world’s vertebrate animal population has declined by 60% since 1970, and efforts to halt biodiversity loss are a “managed decline” at best, according to a new report.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The Living Planet Report by the <a href=\"https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/2018-10/LPR2018_Full%20Report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">World Wide Fund for Nature (WWF)</a> highlights “overexploitation of species, agriculture and land conversion” as the main drivers of population decline. Climate change is also noted as a factor.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fHpsu226Lfsa8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"news_sf_1222\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"news_sf_1222\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/news/sf\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",site:\"trb.nydn\",\r\nslug:\"ny-news-wwf-efforts-stop-loss-decline-20181030\",cid:\"109518568\",at:\"WorldWildlifeFund\",kw:\"seabird,WWF,nature,population,Earth,plastic,lpus,rate,biodiversity,stomach,Lambertini,generation,decline,species,extinction,study,overexploitation,world,choice,%decline,wwf,development,LDRA,land,freshwater\",tg:\"EnvironmentandNature\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The latest Living Planet Index (LPI) — which measures the worldwide population of thousands of amphibians, birds, fish, mammals, and reptiles — shows an average 60% decline in population sizes between 1970 and 2014. This is seen most prominently in Central and South America, with an 89% decline in population. Freshwater species declined 83% according to the Freshwater LPI.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“The evidence becomes stronger every day that humanity’s survival depends on our natural systems, yet we continue to destroy the health of nature at an alarming rate. It’s clear that efforts to stem the loss of biodiversity have not worked and business as usual will amount to, at best, a continued, managed decline,” WWF wrote in the report.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001435\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001435\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f5kez81iLfsa8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"11377\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089988\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Currently, 25% of land on the globe is not impacted by human activity, according to the Land Degradation and Restoration Assessment (LDRA) — a number that experts fear could drop to 10% by 2050.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“We are the first generation that has a clear picture of the value of nature and the grave situation we are facing. We may also be the last generation that can do something about it,” WWF wrote.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>A decade-long study of the loggerhead turtle showed 35% of the analyzed species had ingested debris, nearly all which was plastic. Another study showed 90% of seabirds have plastic fragments in their stomachs, an increase from just 5% of seabirds in 1960. By 2050, it is estimated plastic will be found in the stomachs of 99% of all seabirds if no changes are made.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“Current rates of species extinction are 100 to 1,000 times higher than the background rate, the standard rate of extinction in Earth’s history before human pressure became a prominent factor,” the report said.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f0CEgBPqLfsa8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"17400\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089988\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Many environmental changes have been brought by the Great Acceleration — where the world’s population has grown 7 times as large since 1800, and the economy grown 30 times as large. The last 50 years have caused increased demand for energy, land and water because of economic development, which has impacted the operating systems of Earth.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“We all have a role to play in reversing the loss of nature – but time is running out. Between now and 2020 we have a unique opportunity to influence the shape of global agreements and targets on biodiversity, climate and sustainable development – for a positive future for nature and people,” WWF said.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>In 2020, the world will review progress on “sustainable development” through the Convention on Biological Diversity, the Paris Agreement, and the Sustainable Development Goals. Director general of WWF International Marco Lambertini said at that time, the world should “embrace a new global deal for nature and people.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“There is no excuse for inaction. We can no longer ignore the warning signs; doing so would be at our own peril. What we need now is the will to act – and act quickly,” Lambertini said.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-yieldmo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"4\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_1610965632225229372\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_1610965632225229372\");if(true)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el})}});</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Experts say limiting global warming to 1.5 degrees Celsius, cleaning pollution from the environment, and finding and using more sustainable resources are key to limiting biodiversity loss.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“Today, we still have a choice. We can be the founders of a global movement that changed our relationship with the planet, that saw us secure a future for all life on Earth, including our own. Or we can be the generation that had its chance and failed to act; that let Earth slip away. The choice is ours. Together we can make it happen for nature and for people,” Lambertini said.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> <ul class=\"trb_ar_rt\" data-c-typename=\"article\"> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"World Wildlife Fund\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/world-wildlife-fund/\">World Wildlife Fund</a> </li> </ul> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/qyVx8T1Nwsp0R1RWvWIkksBm50c=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bd87e77/turbine/ny-1540914800-6s9zzw6moy-snap-image', '2018-10-31', 'The Forecaddie', 'animal'),
(8, 3, 'Reese\'s sets up \'candy converter\' vending machine that swaps out unwanted Halloween candy for peanut butter cups', 'Reese’s set up a “candy converter” vending machine in New York City where people can trade in their unwanted Halloween candy for peanut butter cups.', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix col full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">No tricks — just some treats!</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Reese’s set up a “candy converter” vending machine in New York City where people can trade their unwanted Halloween candy for peanut butter cups.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"faYP0h1paDsa8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"news_sf_1052\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"news_sf_1052\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/news/sf\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",site:\"trb.nydn\",\r\nslug:\"ny-news-reeses-unwanted-halloween-candy-20181031\",cid:\"109532460\",at:\"Halloween\",kw:\"candy,Reese,machine,Halloween,Lingeris,reese,converter,cup,trick,Unreal,Square,halloweencandy,Halloweencandy,enthusiast,East,disappointment,slot,peanutbuttercup,response,candyconverter,excitement,halloween,lingeris,peanut,behalf\",tg:\"\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“Disappointment goes in. Reese’s cups come out,” according to a video from the candy corporation.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"raw_html\" class=\"card card-pull-center collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"element element-rawhtml \"> <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/m89djlGgzIQ?enablejsapi=1\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" id=\"1541090043360_TBOtherPlayer_10\"></iframe><script id=\"snap_blurb_ratios\">var parentDoc=parent.document.body,resizeFrame=function(){var e=[],t=\"none\";parentDoc.clientWidth<420?(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-small\"),t=\"block\"):(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-small\"),t=\"none\");for(var a=0;a<e.length;a++)e[a].style.display=t;parentDoc.clientWidth>=420&&parentDoc.clientWidth<840?(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-medium\"),t=\"block\"):(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-medium\"),t=\"none\");for(var a=0;a<e.length;a++)e[a].style.display=\r\nt;parentDoc.clientWidth>=840?(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-large\"),t=\"block\"):(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-large\"),t=\"none\");for(var a=0;a<e.length;a++)e[a].style.display=t};parent.window.addEventListener(\"resize\",resizeFrame,!1);</script></div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The vending machine is located on Fifth Avenue between Washington Square North and East 8th Street — near Washington Square Park. People will be able to swap out candy from 4 to 9 p.m. Up to 10,000 pieces of candy will be distributed.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>People can insert their unwanted candy in a slot on the machine, and the machine dispenses peanut butter cups below.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>According to a survey conducted on behalf of Reese’s, 90% of Americans said they wished they could swap out their Halloween candy.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“Let’s be honest, we’ve all received Halloween candy that we don’t want, so Reese’s is saving Halloween this year with its very own Candy Exchange Vending Machine,” said Hershey spokesperson Anna Lingeris.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001435\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001435\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fq3owl18bDsa8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"12697\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089988\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Lingeris said the response to the converter has been “incredible. Unreal. Amazing.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Twitter users shared excitement over the vending machine.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"oembed_response\" class=\"card card-pull-center collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"element element-oembed oembed-twitter\"> <twitterwidget class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" id=\"twitter-widget-0\" style=\"position: static; visibility: visible; display: block; transform: rotate(0deg); max-width: 100%; width: 500px; min-width: 220px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\" data-tweet-id=\"1057645437870637056\"></twitterwidget> <script async=\"\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"oembed_response\" class=\"card card-pull-center collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"element element-oembed oembed-twitter\"> <twitterwidget class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" id=\"twitter-widget-1\" style=\"position: static; visibility: visible; display: block; transform: rotate(0deg); max-width: 100%; width: 500px; min-width: 220px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\" data-tweet-id=\"1057310132357476357\"></twitterwidget> <script async=\"\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"oembed_response\" class=\"card card-pull-center collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"element element-oembed oembed-twitter\"> <twitterwidget class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" id=\"twitter-widget-2\" style=\"position: static; visibility: visible; display: block; transform: rotate(0deg); max-width: 100%; width: 500px; min-width: 220px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\" data-tweet-id=\"1057481306785886209\"></twitterwidget> <script async=\"\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>For those eagerly awaiting the possibility of more “candy converters” around the country next year, Reese’s enthusiasts will have to wait and see what the next spooky season holds.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“We’ve had an overwhelming response so stay tuned to see what Halloween 2019 will bring,” said Lingeris.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f03rleMwbDsa8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"16477\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089988\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“Come see us today and get your Reese’s! We know you want some!”</p> </div></div> <div class=\"card card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark spaced spaced-top spaced-md\"> <div class=\"card-content card-header flex-container-row align-items-center\">Related Gallery</div> </div> <div data-type=\"gallery\" class=\"card card-pull-center card-captioned collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark spaced spaced-bottom spaced-md\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-gallery\" data-pb-name=\"Article gallery\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"pb-56990\"><div tabindex=\"0\" class=\"gallery slider popup\"><div class=\"gallery-photo-container\"><div class=\"aspect-ratio-container gallery-phot