(11, 5, 'Justin Timberlake wrote \'Cry Me a River\' amid Britney Spears breakup in just two hours', 'Justin Timberlake opens up about his song \"Cry Me a River\" in his new book.', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">Justin Timberlake only needed a couple hours to write one of the biggest — and most personal — songs of his career.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The pop star revealed he churned out “Cry Me a River,” the breakup ballad widely believed to be about Britney Spears, extremely quickly.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f0ztCXDl8Q8j8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"entertainment_music_1982\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"entertainment_music_1982\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/entertainment/music\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"ent\",\r\napv:\"false\",site:\"trb.nydn\",slug:\"ny-ent-justin-timberlake-cry-me-river-20181101\",cid:\"109544227\",at:\"JustinTimberlake,BritneySpears,JessicaBiel\",kw:\"Timberlake,Spears,song,timberlake,Cry,river,producer,feeling,Timbaland,spears,Hindsight,burnednow,Silas,cry,book,pop,Grammy,lyric,edition,studio,career,actress,concert,timbaland,bridge\",tg:\"\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“I’ve been scorned. I’ve been pissed off. I wrote ‘Cry Me a River’ in two hours. I didn’t plan on writing it,” Timberlake writes in his new book, “Hindsight: &amp; All the Things I Can’t See in Front of Me,” according to <a href=\"https://people.com/music/justin-timberlake-wrote-cry-me-a-river-2-hours-britney-spears/\" target=\"_blank\">People</a>.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“The feelings I had were so strong that I had to write it, and I translated my feelings into a form where people could listen and, hopefully, relate to it,” Timberlake continued. “People heard me and they understood it because we’ve all been there.”</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001400\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001400\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001400\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001400\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001400\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fBFROd1y8Q8j8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"15162\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089976\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The former *NSYNC vocalist does not identify the subject of the jaded track in the book. He released the song in November 2002, several months after he and Spears called it quits.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The popular song features bitter lyrics such as, “The bridges were burned/Now it\'s your turn, to cry.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"image\" class=\"card card-pull-center card-captioned collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <figure class=\"\"> <div class=\"full-width img-container \"> <img class=\"b-lazy full-width b-loaded\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake and Britney Spears are seen in early 2002. His song &quot;Cry Me a River&quot; is widely rumored to be about their breakup.\" src=\"https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/r0J_1pehUBdwIFUviWfcl8I_SeY=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bdb1309/turbine/ny-1541083908-e3e9b2a3lp-snap-image\"> </div> <figcaption class=\"caption-text spaced spaced-top spaced-sm flex-container-row justify-space-between \"> <div>Justin Timberlake and Britney Spears are seen in early 2002. His song \"Cry Me a River\" is widely rumored to be about their breakup. (J. Emilio Flores / Getty Images)</div> </figcaption> </figure> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The source of Timberlake’s pain in the “Cry Me a River” music video, meanwhile, is a blonde woman who resembles Spears.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Timberlake and the song’s producer, Timbaland, <a href=\"https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2011/12/22/justin-timberlake-britney-spears-cry-me-a-river_n_1164520.html\" target=\"_blank\">seemed to confirm</a> the song is about Spears during an edition of “E! True Hollywood Story” that aired in 2011. In the special, the producer says Timberlake was furious after seeing Spears speak about him at one of her concerts.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f05dIYMG8Q8j8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"15534\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089976\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>\"I was on a phone call that was not the most enjoyable phone call,” Timberlake recalls on the show. “I walked into the studio and (Timbaland) could tell I was visibly angry.\"</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The song netted Timberlake a Grammy — for best male pop vocal performance — in 2004.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Timberlake, 37, began dating Jessica Biel in 2007 and has been married to the actress since 2012. They have a 3-year-old son together named Silas.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> <ul class=\"trb_ar_rt\" data-c-typename=\"article\"> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"Justin Timberlake\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/justin-timberlake/\">Justin Timberlake</a> </li> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"Britney Spears\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/britney-spears/\">Britney Spears</a> </li> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"Jessica Biel\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/jessica-biel/\">Jessica Biel</a> </li> </ul> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/_0wwC8C_JDtvfZmF9a23IC3i0s0=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bdb129e/turbine/ny-1541083799-3v24spqnt0-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Peter Sblendorio', 'Justin Timberlake, music'),
(12, 5, 'Rihanna reportedly turned down Super Bowl halftime show in support of Colin Kaepernick', 'The “Work” singer reportedly turned down the NFL’s offer to headline the Super Bowl halftime show in support of Colin Kaepernick, who hasn’t found his way onto a roster since he kneeled on the sidelines .', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">Rihanna will stop the music after all.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The “Work” singer reportedly turned down the NFL’s offer to headline the Super Bowl halftime show in support of Colin Kaepernick, who hasn’t found his way onto a roster since he kneeled on the sidelines during the National Anthem in protest of police brutality.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fufOlJ1CVr9j8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"entertainment_music_565\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"entertainment_music_565\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/entertainment/music\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",\r\napv:\"false\",site:\"trb.nydn\",slug:\"ny-ent-20181018\",cid:\"108462931\",at:\"\",kw:\"NFL,Rihanna,nfl,rihanna,kaepernick,apes-t,Jay-Z,endzone,Maroon,song,rep,music,sideline,grievance,Bowl,singer,Super,Fox,roster,performer,headline,offer,stance,rumor,stadium\",tg:\"Football,Music,PopCulture,Celebrity\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“The NFL and Fox really wanted Rihanna to be next year’s performer in Atlanta,” a source told <a href=\"https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/rihanna-declined-super-bowl-liii-halftime-show-offer/\" target=\"_blank\">Us Weekly</a>. “They offered it to her, but she said no because of the kneeling controversy. She doesn’t agree with the NFL’s stance.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"image\" class=\"card card-pull-center card-captioned collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <figure class=\"\"> <div class=\"full-width img-container \"> <img class=\"b-lazy full-width b-loaded\" alt=\"Colin Kaepernick sued the NFL owners last year for colluding against him.\" src=\"https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/xDqqqLxjVoulmgteYWvYVNLVlh4=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bc90a3c/turbine/ny-1539901997-23so4yyfou-snap-image\"> </div> <figcaption class=\"caption-text spaced spaced-top spaced-sm flex-container-row justify-space-between \"> <div>Colin Kaepernick sued the NFL owners last year for colluding against him. (Steven Senne / AP)</div> </figcaption> </figure> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>In October 2017, Kaepernick filed a grievance against NFL owners, alleging that they had colluded to keep him out of the league for causing a stir.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001400\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001400\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001400\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001400\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001400\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"flnHq11UVr9j8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"10827\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089976\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Rumors circulated last year that Jay-Z had similarly turned down a halftime show and he seemingly confirmed the news in a recent song, “Apes—t.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“I said no to the Super Bowl: you need me, I don\'t need you,” he raps in the song. “Every night we in the endzone, tell the NFL we in stadiums too.\"</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Instead of Rihanna, Super Bowl LIII has reportedly landed Maroon 5 for the Feb. 4 game.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Reps for Rihanna and the NFL did not immediately return requests for comment.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fE61Hg12Wr9j8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"6273\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089976\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/7So63FTgfmGNwQQAiZBRVIEdpXA=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bc90722/turbine/ny-1539901200-1ulmmkuhlc-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Kate Feldman', 'Rihanna, scandal'),
(13, 4, 'Your sea salt is polluted with microplastics', 'Microplastics have been getting mixed in with commercial food-grade salts, especially sea salts, according to a new study.', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">Chances are, you’re seasoning your food with a pinch of plastic.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>There’s a global problem with microplastics — small plastic fragments less than five millimeters in length — getting mixed in with commercial food-grade salts, according to a new study.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"feISSe2NU1bj8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"lifestyle_eats_1523\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"lifestyle_eats_1523\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/lifestyle/eats\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",\r\nsite:\"trb.nydn\",slug:\"ny-fea-sea-salt-microplastics-study-20181017\",cid:\"108451048\",at:\"\",kw:\"salt,microplastic,plastic,amount,millimeter,pinch,seasalt,study,seawater,fragment,Technology,region,food,pollution,length,indicator,Seasalt,continent,river,brand,county,chance,Sea,research,environment\",tg:\"EnvironmentandNature\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The <a href=\"https://pubs.acs.org/doi/pdf/10.1021/acs.est.8b04180\" target=\"_blank\">research</a>, published in the scientific journal Environmental Science &amp; Technology, looked at 39 different salt brands, including 28 sea salt brands from 16 different countries or regions on six continents.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>More than 90% of sampled salts were found to contain microplastics. Sea salts were the most likely to be contaminated with plastics, followed by lake salt and rock salt.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001405\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001405\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f0b0rwNZU1bj8r\"> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Sea salts produced in Asian counties — which, as the study notes, is “a hot spot of global plastic pollution” — had high amounts of plastic compared with other regions. And the amounts of microplastics found in sea salts were linked with contamination levels in surrounding rivers and seawater.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The study concluded that sea salt can be a good indicator of how polluted with plastic surrounding marine environments are.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/sR6VZSeyQT9kXLYZIM_AumRqq0Q=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bc7a4b5/turbine/ny-1539810468-73lrbwn707-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Gina Salamone', 'Lamborghini , Aventador'),
(14, 4, 'Beer sold in 77-packs has Maryland\'s comptroller accusing Anheuser-Busch of promoting binge drinking', 'Anheuser-Busch sold 77-packs of its Natural Light beer near a college campus and Maryland\'s comptroller isn\'t thrilled.', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">Beer sold in 77-packs around one college campus is causing more than a little brew-haha, er, brouhaha.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Maryland’s chief financial officer is accusing Anheuser-Busch of promoting binge drinking to college students thanks to its limited time 77-packs of Natural Light beer that were sold in stores in College Park, Maryland. The city is home to the University of Maryland.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f9pkjx16pDbj8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"lifestyle_eats_802\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"lifestyle_eats_802\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/lifestyle/eats\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",\r\nsite:\"trb.nydn\",slug:\"ny-fea-beer-77-packs-maryland-comptroller-binge-drinking-20181016\",cid:\"108435165\",at:\"\",kw:\"Maryland,77-pack,maryland,beer,bingedrinking,binge,Anheuser-Busch,drink,student,brew-haha,brouhaha,study,Beer,wusa9,Franchot,Brody,drinking,keg,alcohol,University,impact,Journal,timeframe,collegepark,anheuser-busch\",tg:\"\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“They’re obviously promoting binge drinking by young people,” Maryland comptroller Peter Franchot said, according to CBS affiliate <a href=\"https://www.wusa9.com/article/news/local/a-77-pack-beer-maker-accused-of-promoting-binge-drinking-at-university-of-maryland/65-604568306\" target=\"_blank\">WUSA9</a>.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Natural Light, a reduced-calorie pilsner launched by Anheuser-Busch in 1977, announced on Twitter on Oct. 5 that it would be selling the 77-packs for a short time only in College Park to celebrate its creation year.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001405\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001405\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fBcz7A1ipDbj8r\"> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"oembed_response\" class=\"card card-pull-left collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"element element-oembed oembed-twitter\"> <twitterwidget class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" id=\"twitter-widget-0\" style=\"position: static; visibility: visible; display: block; transform: rotate(0deg); max-width: 100%; width: 500px; min-width: 220px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\" data-tweet-id=\"1048275293675376641\"></twitterwidget> <script async=\"\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The keg-like packs sold out quickly, according to WUSA9.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Franchot, who has advocated for locally made craft beers to promote job growth in Maryland, is also calling for an investigation into large brewing companies bribing Maryland legislators with campaign contributions and favors, the news outlet reports.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“Corporate beer manufacturers claim to care about the public health impacts of alcohol, but the message they send by selling a 77-pack of beer designed to look like a keg in a college town shows they care more about their bottom line than the negative impacts of binge drinking,” Alan Brody, a spokesman for the Maryland comptroller, told the Daily News.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Brody added that details on a potential investigation are still coming together.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f74xtZ1qpDbj8r\"> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Binge drinking on college campuses is common for as many as 40% of students, according to a study in the August volume of the <a href=\"http://jaoa.org/article.aspx?articleid=2687950\" target=\"_blank\">Journal of the American Osteopathic Association</a>. The study included a sample of nearly 300 students and defined binge drinking as when women consume at least four drinks in a two-hour time frame and men have at least five drinks in that same time frame.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The study found that changes in the students’ physical environment, like reducing exposure to alcohol, would help curtail binge drinking.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/2raTgut98RKKcmazmSzf_o1Gbpg=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bc60129/turbine/ny-1539703072-fyu4ehhl4m-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Gina Salamone', 'beer, Maryland'),
(15, 4, 'The most offensive-sounding pumpkin spice product has arrived as a hummus shake', 'Watch out, world! Hummus & Pita Co. has launched the Pumpkin Spice Hummus Shake. ', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">Game over. The most offensive-sounding pumpkin spice product has officially arrived.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Here to add some fright to your fall is the Pumpkin Spice Hummus Shake. Grab it — or avoid it — at <a href=\"https://www.hummusandpitas.com/Location-THPC-6th-Avenue-NY/Default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">The Hummus &amp; Pita Co.</a>, where it’s available for $5 at all three of the chickpea chain’s Manhattan locations and its Danbury, Connecticut outpost.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fsmDB02SKzej8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"lifestyle_eats_208\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"lifestyle_eats_208\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/lifestyle/eats\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",\r\nsite:\"trb.nydn\",slug:\"ny-fea-pumpkin-spice-hummus-shake-20181008\",cid:\"107529803\",at:\"\",kw:\"chickpea,Hummus,ave,tahinus,hummus,Pumpkin,shake,pumpkin,spice,garlic,applesauce,oats,dessert,Danbury,Pesso,Pita,fright,cinnamonpitachip,gaga,Tribeca,butter,vanilla,latte,cream,sub\",tg:\"Restaurants\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>A <a href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/life-style/eats/hummus-milkshakes-ready-not-article-1.3966306\" target=\"_blank\">regular hummus shake</a> launched at the company in May as a blend of chickpeas, tahini, banana, dates, and almond milk. This seasonal upgrade is made with all-natural pumpkin puree, chickpeas, tahini, almond butter, quick oats, sugar-free applesauce and vanilla, and is topped with The Hummus &amp; Pita Co.’s own pumpkin spice mix. Order it with or without whipped cream.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Some might be scared off at the idea of a sweet shake laden with hummus — the savory snack dip normally made with chickpeas mashed with oil, lemon juice, tahini and gasp, garlic. But this shake, available through Thanksgiving weekend, skips the garlic and subs in the more mild and sweet flavors of almond butter, oats and applesauce.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001405\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001405\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001405\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fXNQZV12Lzej8r\"> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The company is also selling Pumpkin Pie Dessert Hummus, made with similar ingredients, until the new year. It’ll cost you $4.55 for a small, $5.45 for a medium or $6.45 for a large.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“We do make our dessert hummus with chickpeas, and it\'s healthy like traditional hummus,” The Hummus &amp; Pita Co. founder Dave Pesso told the Daily News. “But that\'s where the similarities end. I originally crafted the recipe as a healthy dessert for my daughter. It\'s a guilt-free and delicious treat you can have every day, as it\'s packed with protein from chickpeas while being vegan, gluten-free, and dairy-free.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Pesso suggests dipping into the dessert hummus with cinnamon pita chips, pretzels, apples, or just scooping it up with a spoon.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Each fall, pumpkin spice-flavored products invade grocery store shelves and coffee chain latte lineups, pitting those who go gaga for them against those who gag over them. Starbucks’ Pumpkin Spice Latte is a longtime fan favorite, and Trader Joe’s is known for its seemingly unlimited amount of pumpkin spice goods, ranging from Pumpkin Rolls with Pumpkin Spice Icing to Petite Pumpkin Spice Cookies.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f0HJXAN8Lzej8r\"> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>In New York, score the Pumpkin Spice Hummus Shake at these Hummus &amp; Pita Co. locations: Chelsea (585 6th Ave.), Tribeca (79 Chambers St.) and 8th Ave (616 8th Ave.).</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-xxl spaced-bottom hidden-mobile hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/VxCBDTICZ8Uu6MvfM39NR7mLzBc=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bbb89c2/turbine/ny-1539017148-edlc4at2pg-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Gina Salamone', 'pumpkin, health'),
(16, 7, 'Pokemon Go Teases November Bug Field Research Tasks', 'Pokemon goes back to its roots with a celebration of bugs.', '<section class=\"article-body typography-format  typography-format--large\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"js-content-entity-body\" data-ajaxform=\"true\">\r\n                    <p>Pokemon Go has gotten spooky for Halloween, but with November almost upon us Niantic has started to tease the next seasonal event. The company hinted through Twitter that November will be all about catching bugs, with a big reward for completing your marks.</p><p>November will bring Field Research tasks all around Bug-type Pokemon. If you collect enough stamps during the month, you can get a Research Breakthrough and an opportunity to catch a Shedinja. Presumably this means that Nincada and Ninjask would also become available sometime in the month.</p><p>Shedinja is a Bug- and Ghost-type Pokemon that first appeared in <a href=\"/pokemon-ruby-version/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-3337\">Pokemon Ruby</a> and <a href=\"/pokemon-ruby-version/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-3337\">Sapphire</a>. It\'s the evolved form of Nincada, which would populate into an empty spot once that Pokemon involved into a Ninjask. The idea was that the exoskeleton of the Nincada would become its own individual Pokemon once the Ninjask emerged from it into the evolved form.</p><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/pokemongoapp/status/1055942177182883841?s=21\"><twitterwidget class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" id=\"twitter-widget-0\" style=\"position: static; visibility: visible; display: block; transform: rotate(0deg); width: 500px; margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; min-width: 220px;\" data-tweet-id=\"1055942177182883841\"></twitterwidget><script async=\"\" src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></div><p>This means you have a few more days to complete the <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/pokemon-go-halloween-event-going-on-now-features-f/1100-6462728/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6462728\">special Halloween event</a> going on now. This year the event is debuting Drifloon, Drifblim, Stunky, and Skuntank--all Ghost and Dark type, appropriately enough. The store also added some new spooky gear, like a Gengar backpack. The new Special Research quest line for the month revolves around Spiritomb. And during the Halloween event, you can get double Candy for capturing Pokemon.</p><div id=\"incontent-ad-wrap\" class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\"><div id=\"incontent-ad\" class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad\" style=\"display: none;\" data-google-query-id=\"CLHfmLW8t94CFRgcKgod_1oBuA\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" srcdoc=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom;\" data-google-container-id=\"5\" data-load-complete=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></div><p>A Gym Raid battle this month introduces Giratina, the first Gen 4 Legendary in the game. That will last through November 20. Plus the next Community Day, scheduled for November 10, will feature Cyndaquil, the <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/pokemon-gold-version/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-1628\">Pokemon Gold and Silver</a> starter.</p>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        \r\n  \r\n  \r\n                                    <dl class=\"news-related\"><dt><i class=\"icon icon-tags\"></i>  Filed under:</dt><dd><a href=\"/pokemon-go/\">Pokemon GO</a></dd><dd><a href=\"/platform/mobile/\">Mobile</a></dd></dl>        \r\n        \r\n          <div class=\"content-slug content-slug--article\">\r\n    <p><i>Got a news tip or want to contact us direc