(18, 7, 'Ebay Pre-Black Friday Sale Offers Deals On Games And Hardware', 'The retail and auction site Ebay has announced a lengthy sale with some discounts on games and tech rotating daily. It lasts through November 11, and already features discounts on hardware, consoles, and recent game releases.', '<section class=\"article-body typography-format  typography-format--large\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"js-content-entity-body\" data-ajaxform=\"true\">\r\n                    <p>The retail and auction site Ebay has announced a lengthy sale with some discounts on games and tech rotating daily. It lasts through November 11, and already features discounts on hardware, consoles, and recent game releases.</p><p>The current deals listed on the <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/deals#r1_i7\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">official site</a> include a white Xbox One S 1 TB for $240 and a refurbished grey Nintendo Switch for $275. You can also pick up <a href=\"/red-dead-redemption-2/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-458780\">Red Dead Redemption 2</a> on Xbox One for $48, or <a href=\"/marvels-spider-man/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-455396\">Spider-Man</a> for $50.</p><p>In hardware and tech, the deals list a Samsung 50\" LED 4K TV with HDR for $420, and an AMD Ryzen 7 1700X Desktop Processor 8-Core for $170. The main page has a full section for PC accessories and another for laptops and tablets with lots of offerings on display--particularly Chromebooks and monitors. A Microsoft Surface Go is only discounted ten bucks to $540, but comes with a $50 Xbox gift card.</p><p>According to the <a href=\"https://www.ebayinc.com/stories/news/ebay-helps-you-sleigh-holiday-shopping-early-with-first-minute-deals/\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">promotion</a>, we can expect more game deals next Monday, November 5, with the theme \"Game Time.\" Those include a Neon Red/Blue Nintendo Switch, HyperX Cloud II Red Gaming Headset for $60, and HP 27\" Edge to Edge HD Gaming Monitor for $140.</p><div id=\"incontent-ad-wrap\" class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\"><div id=\"incontent-ad\" class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"COv49Ka9t94CFZBtYAodWa8LZQ\" style=\"display: none;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4\" width=\"321\" height=\"31\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" srcdoc=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom;\" data-google-container-id=\"5\" data-load-complete=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></div><p>Other deals are smaller but notable. A few models of Apple iPhones are discounted by $20 today, and the Apple Watch Series 4 will be discounted by $10 on November 7. If you\'re a gadget enthusiast, you may want to check back on November 3 for deals like a Remo smart security camera for $150, or the Ecobee Smart Thermostat for $200.</p><p>These discounts appear primed to let users get a jump on <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/black-friday/\">Black Friday</a>, which is certain to have a wealth of its own deals incoming as well. We\'ve already seen <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/targets-early-black-friday-deals-announced/1100-6462947/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6462947\">Target\'s</a> and more are on the way.</p>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        \r\n  \r\n  \r\n                      \r\n                            \r\n        \r\n          \r\n\r\n      </section>', 'https://static.gamespot.com/uploads/screen_small/1585/15855271/3458163-reddeadredemption-gameplay-promo-2.jpg', '2018-11-03', 'Steve Watts', 'Ebay, Sale'),
(19, 7, 'Smash Bros. Ultimate DLC Will Add More New Characters, Stages After Piranha Plant DLC', 'Today\'s Super Smash Bros. Ultimate presentation filled out the rest of the roster and revealed all of the fighters that will be in the game upon release.', '<section class=\"article-body typography-format  typography-format--large\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"js-content-entity-body\" data-ajaxform=\"true\">\r\n                    <p>Today\'s <a href=\"/super-smash-bros-ultimate/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-480957\">Super Smash Bros. Ultimate</a> presentation filled out the rest of the roster and revealed all of the fighters that will be in the game upon release. But more are coming, as the presentation also noted that more <a href=\"/articles/all-super-smash-bros-ultimate-characters-confirmed/1100-6462936/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6462936\">fighters</a> will be added post-launch as DLC.</p><p>Each fighter pack will include one fighter, one stage, and multiple music tracks, for $6. Nintendo is planning to release five packs, and you can purchase a bundle \"Fighters Pass\" for $25 that will include all five fighters, five stages, and all the music tracks. Nintendo noted that it hasn\'t begun active development on the fighters yet so it may take up to a year to complete the full Fighter\'s Pass. Purchasing the Fighter\'s Pass will also get you an outfit based on Rex from <a href=\"/xenoblade-chronicles-2/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-461277\">Xenoblade Chronicles 2</a>.</p><p>Another piece of post-launch content is coming for free. <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-smash-bros-ultimate-has-a-very-unexpected-fr/1100-6462933/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6462933\">Piranha Plant</a> will be available for free for early purchasers. If you buy Super Smash Bros. Ultimate digitally or register your physical copy by January 31, 2019, you\'ll get the fighter at no cost around February 2019. It will be available for purchase separately sometime later.</p><p>Today\'s presentation revealed the final two roster characters: <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-smash-bros-ultimate-reveals-final-two-new-ch/1100-6462928/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6462928\">Ken and Incineroar</a>. It also took the wraps off the <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-smash-bros-ultimate-announces-new-spirits-mo/1100-6462931/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6462931\">final mode, Spirits</a>, which allows you to take part in special challenges to earn equippable buffs for your characters. This also serves as the story for the game, as Nintendo teased that there will be a plot explanation for the characters being turned into apparitions. You can read about every announcement and watch the highlights of the Direct in our <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-smash-bros-ultimate-november-direct-new-char/1100-6462944/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6462944\">news round-up</a>.</p><div id=\"incontent-ad-wrap\" class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\"><div id=\"incontent-ad\" class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad\" style=\"display: none;\" data-google-query-id=\"CKHF8sy-t94CFdV6iwod9TwH2A\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/asia-gamespot/news_4\" width=\"321\" height=\"31\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" srcdoc=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom;\" data-google-container-id=\"5\" data-load-complete=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></div><p>Smash Bros. Ultimate launches on December 7. Check out our <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-smash-bros-ultimates-release-date-and-switch/1100-6459374/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6459374\">pre-order guide</a> for more details.</p>\r\n                                          </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        \r\n  \r\n  \r\n                                            \r\n        \r\n          \r\n\r\n      </section>', 'https://static.gamespot.com/uploads/screen_small/1585/15855271/3457876-3400595-smash_thumb.jpg', '2018-11-03', 'Steve Watts', 'DLC, Smash Bros'),
(20, 1, 'Japanese island vanishes for good under the waves', 'A small, uninhabited island off the coast of Japan has vanished for good and no one seemed to notice — or even know exactly when it happened!', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">A small, uninhabited island off the coast of Japan has vanished for good and no one seemed to notice — or even know exactly when it happened!</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Esanbe Hanakita Kojima, located just about about one-third of a mile off the coast off the Japanese island of Hokkaido, is believed to have permanently slid underneath the seas, reported <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/nov/02/japanese-island-disappears-esanbe-hanakita-kojima\" target=\"_blank\">The Guardian</a>.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fCdFRK1XmGsj8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"news_world_462\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"news_world_462\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/news/world\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",site:\"trb.nydn\",\r\nslug:\"ny-news-japan-island-disappears-20181102\",cid:\"109560963\",at:\"Japan\",kw:\"island,Japan,esanbe,coast,japan,sea,Hokkaido,climatologist,islet,Territories,Soviets,isle,one-third,Guardian,fisherman,fishing,winter,inch,wind,boat,one,dispute,Russia,mile,size\",tg:\"Luxury,EnvironmentandNature\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The Japanese Coast Guard said the island protruded about 55 inches from the sea surface back in 1987. Leading climatologists believe over the last 31 years the islet has been been eroded by Sea of Okhotsk drift ice and wind every winter.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Seasoned fishermen mentioned they steered clear of the island decades ago because navigational systems believed it was an undersea reef.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001435\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001435\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fmtAfF18nGsj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"6943\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089988\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Esanbe is one of 158 uninhabited islands off the Japanese coast. It is situated in the Northern Territories, an area of dispute between Japan and Russia. The islands were snatched from Japan by the Soviets after World War II ended.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Local residents were made aware Esanbe could be gone in September after an author of a book of Japanese hidden islands mentioned the possibility. Boats from a fishing cooperative confirmed the isle was no longer visible.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>If authorities rule the island is no more, it will actually change the official size of Japan — but only by several thousand square feet.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>In October, the Hawaiian spit East Island was wiped away for good by Hurricane Walaka.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> <ul class=\"trb_ar_rt\" data-c-typename=\"article\"> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"Japan\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/japan/\">Japan</a> </li> </ul> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fgOsQv1gnGsj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"14691\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089988\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/gk4Pul7iNdSNf7Enra9JpEUTb0c=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bdce667/turbine/ny-1541203552-0jpknx8nle-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Storm Gifford', 'Japanese, disaster'),
(21, 1, 'Telescope observation shows Milky Way\'s black hole — and it\'s \'mind-boggling\'', 'The GRAVITY instrument on the European Southern Observatory’s Very Large Telescope recently discovered new information about the Milky Way’s central supermassive black hole, as illustrated here. (ESO/Gravity Consortium/L. Calçada)', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">Gas blobs were pulled into the supermassive black hole at the Milky Way’s center at an incredible speed — and scientists have captured it on a telescope.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>A GRAVITY instrument on the Very Large Telescope (VLTI) array in Chile observed Sagittarius A, the enormous object at the center of the Milky Way, according to a new study <a href=\"https://www.eso.org/public/news/eso1835/\" target=\"_blank\">published Wednesday</a> in the Journal of Astronomy &amp; Astrophysics.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"foglz31DUntj8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"news_world_1589\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"news_world_1589\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/news/world\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",site:\"trb.nydn\",\r\nslug:\"ny-news-telescope-observation-shows-milky-way-black-hole-boggling-20181031\",cid:\"109530886\",at:\"AstronomyandAstrophysics,Space\",kw:\"flare,hole,Pfuhl,telescope,gravity,scientist,speed,VLTI,Astrophysics,Telescope,Astronomy,center,MPE,Journal,study,Milky,MilkyWay,milkyway,simulation,pull,array,Chile,object,Way,sensitivity\",tg:\"PhysicalScience\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>European Southern Observatory scientists say this is the first time material has been seen moving around the point of no return.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>\"It’s mind-boggling to actually witness material orbiting a massive black hole at 30% of the speed of light,\" Oliver Pfuhl, a scientist at the MPE, said in a statement.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001435\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001435\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f0sXRlxNUntj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"2358\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089988\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"raw_html\" class=\"card card-pull-center collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"element element-rawhtml \"> <iframe src=\"https://gfycat.com/ifr/FailingNewImperialeagle\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\"></iframe><p> <a href=\"https://gfycat.com/FailingNewImperialeagle\">via Gfycat</a></p><script id=\"snap_blurb_ratios\">var parentDoc=parent.document.body,resizeFrame=function(){var e=[],t=\"none\";parentDoc.clientWidth<420?(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-small\"),t=\"block\"):(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-small\"),t=\"none\");for(var a=0;a<e.length;a++)e[a].style.display=t;parentDoc.clientWidth>=420&&parentDoc.clientWidth<840?(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-medium\"),t=\"block\"):(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-medium\"),t=\"none\");for(var a=0;a<e.length;a++)e[a].style.display=\r\nt;parentDoc.clientWidth>=840?(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-large\"),t=\"block\"):(e=document.getElementsByClassName(\"lat-embed-large\"),t=\"none\");for(var a=0;a<e.length;a++)e[a].style.display=t};parent.window.addEventListener(\"resize\",resizeFrame,!1);</script></div> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001435\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001435\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fPE1832TUntj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"5225\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089988\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>NASA describes a <a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/audience/forstudents/k-4/stories/nasa-knows/what-is-a-black-hole-k4.html\" target=\"_blank\">black hole</a> as a place in space where the pull of gravity is so strong that light can’t even escape.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Black holes are invisible, but space telescopes can see how stars nearby act differently than others.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>\"GRAVITY’s tremendous sensitivity has allowed us to observe the accretion processes in real time in unprecedented detail,” Pfuhl explained.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f0aFO1T0Vntj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"15690\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089988\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"oembed_response\" class=\"card card-pull-center collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <div class=\"element element-oembed oembed-twitter\"> <twitterwidget class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" id=\"twitter-widget-0\" style=\"position: static; visibility: visible; display: block; transform: rotate(0deg); max-width: 100%; width: 500px; min-width: 220px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\" data-tweet-id=\"825433476207955971\"></twitterwidget> <script async=\"\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Pfuhl called the unexpected finding a “lucky coincidence,” after noticing three bright flares by the black hole.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The flares are believed to originate from magnetic interactions in the hot gas orbiting near Sagittarius A — and a simulation of the flares has been created thanks to the European Southern Observatory.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>\"The result is a resounding confirmation of the massive black hole paradigm,” said Reinhard Genzel, of the Max Planck Institute for Extraterrestrial Physics, who led the study.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> <ul class=\"trb_ar_rt\" data-c-typename=\"article\"> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"Astronomy and Astrophysics\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/astronomy-and-astrophysics/\">Astronomy and Astrophysics</a> </li> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"Space\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/space/\">Space</a> </li> </ul> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/_UFmK4wjjtRSY7_HNUDJPKmV4qQ=/1400x0/arc-anglerfish-arc2-prod-tronc.s3.amazonaws.com/public/5LGPR34XWRES5KPGRHMFCEYBA4.jpg', '2018-11-03', 'Daniel Cinone', 'Gravity, science'),
(22, 1, 'Police halt 2nd migrant group trying to enter Mexico', 'A Mexican federal police helicopter flies close to the Suchiate River, between Mexico and Guatemala, in order to create a downwash force to discourage a new group of Central American migrants bound for the U.S border. ', 'A Mexican federal police helicopter flies close to the Suchiate River, between Mexico and Guatemala, in order to create a downwash force to discourage a new group of Central American migrants bound for the U.S border. ', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/TSfmdjvWhQIt9uJ-2WhS6SNseo0=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bd77713/turbine/ny-1540847369-y3xd22fsbz-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Daniel Cinone', 'Mexical police'),
(23, 1, 'President Trump told former lawyer Michael Cohen that \'black people are too stupid to vote for me\'', 'President Trump\'s former personal attorney says the one-time host of \"The Apprentice\" frequently used offensive and racist language', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">President Trump’s former lawyer says the ex-reality TV star frequently made offensive and racist comments in private — even telling him during the 2016 campaign he believed “black people are too stupid to vote for me.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Michael Cohen told <a href=\"https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2018/11/michael-cohen-trump-racist-language\" target=\"_blank\">Vanity Fair</a> on Friday that he often heard Trump make such comments behind closed doors.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f07MKb3ZEauj8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"news_politics_1575\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"news_politics_1575\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/news/politics\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",\r\nsite:\"trb.nydn\",slug:\"ny-pol-trump-racist-language-michael-cohe-20181102\",cid:\"109558248\",at:\"\",kw:\"Cohen,Trump,trump,cohen,President,Mexico,apprentice,Zampolli,comment,magazine,barrister,boss,mexico,lowlife,accusation,racism,vanilla,rally,head-to-head,midterm,pair,caravan,back-and-forth,News,remark\",tg:\"Veterans,Luxury,CultureandTradition,CongressionalElections,RaceandEthnicity,CommunitiesandSubcultures\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Cohen recounted a discussion he had with the then-presidential candidate at Trump Tower in 2016 in which the one-time Trump confidante noted that the crowd at a rally earlier in the day was largely Caucasian.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“I told Trump that the rally looked vanilla on television. Trump responded, ‘That’s because black people are too stupid to vote for me,’” Cohen told the magazine.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001435\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001435\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f0PNNgmaFauj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"9134\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089988\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Years earlier, shortly after the death of Nelson Mandela, Cohen claims that Trump asked him to, “Name one country run by a black person that’s not a s---hole,” adding, “Name one city.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“I’m not surprised at all,” a source with ties to the White House told the Daily News. “So many people have come forward with similar stories.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Cohen also recalled a trip in the 2000s in which he and Trump were riding in a car riding through a run-down neighborhood in Chicago on the way to a business meeting. Trump took note of his surroundings and said something to the effect of “only the blacks could live like this.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"image\" class=\"card card-pull-center card-captioned collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <figure class=\"\"> <div class=\"full-width img-container \"> <img class=\"b-lazy full-width b-loaded\" alt=\"Michael Cohen, former personal lawyer to President Trump, claims his old boss often used racist language.\" src=\"https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/bEhoTP7j7Pwg-_EyDHkbq3P0xHU=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bdcaf19/turbine/ny-1541189393-bv06ws35nd-snap-image\"> </div> <figcaption class=\"caption-text spaced spaced-top spaced-sm flex-container-row justify-space-between \"> <div>Michael Cohen, former personal lawyer to President Trump, claims his old boss often used racist language. (Craig Ruttle / AP)</div> </figcaption> </figure> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Another racist comment came from Trump when the pair were discussing past seasons of “The Apprentice.”</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f1rQe72iFauj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"19871\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089988\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The two were talking about the show’s first season, which ended with two contestants, Bill Rancic and Kwame Jackson, in a head-to-head.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“Trump was explaining his back-and-forth about not picking Jackson,” an African-American investment manager who had graduated from Harvard Business School, Cohen said. “He said, ‘There’s no way I can let this black f-g win.’”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Cohen told Vanity Fair that, in retrospect, he wished he stopped working for Trump when he heard his old boss’ remarks.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The disgraced barrister pleaded guilty in August to campaign-finance crimes for paying two women to keep quiet about their alleged affairs with Trump ahead of the 2016 election — telling the judge that he did so at the request of his former boss.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-yieldmo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"4\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_1610965632225229372\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_1610965632225229372\");if(true)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el})}});</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>He chose to share his stories now because he “wants to clear his conscience and warn voters about what he sees as the President\'s true nature in advance of the midterm election,” according to the magazine.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Cohen was Trump’s staunchest defenders against such accusations of racism until he took a plea deal and the pair had a falling out.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Paolo Zampolli, a longtime friend of the Trump family who introduced the President to the First Lady, had some harsh words for Cohen.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>“It’s nonsense,\" Zampolli told The News. “I think that this comes from a guy who lost his profession and is trying to make some money for writing a book or something. This is a book-tour start.”</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"5\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fHXXCn1qFauj8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"news_politics_1098\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"news_politics_1098\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/news/politics\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",\r\nsite:\"trb.nydn\",slug:\"ny-pol-trump-racist-language-michael-cohe-20181102\",cid:\"109558248\",at:\"\",kw:\"Cohen,Trump,trump,cohen,President,Mexico,apprentice,Zampolli,comment,magazine,barrister,boss,mexico,lowlife,accusation,racism,vanilla,rally,head-to-head,midterm,pair,caravan,back-and-forth,News,remark\",tg:\"Veterans,Luxury,CultureandTradition,CongressionalElections,RaceandEthnicity,CommunitiesandSubcultures\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Cohen is scheduled to be sentenced in December.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Trump has faced cries of racism from critics since launching his campaign for the White House by decrying “rapists” being sent to the U.S. from Mexico. He recently reupped his anti-immigrant rhetoric in the lead up to the midterms by railing against a caravan of Central American migrants currently marching through Mexico.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Cohen’s claims of racist behavior back up several other reports of Trump’s racist remarks.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Earlier this year, Trump expressed frustration with people coming to the U.S. from Haiti, El Salvador and some parts of Africa, places which he reportedly referred to as “s---hole countries” during a closed-door meeting in the White House.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Former White House staffer and two-time star of Trump’s reality show Omarosa Manigault Newman accused the President of using racist language in book released this past summer.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Manigault Newman alleged that Trump was recorded multiple times using the n-word during filming of “The Apprentice.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Trump responded to the accusations by calling Manigault Newman a \"dog\" and a \"crazed, crying lowlife.”</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p><em>With Chris Sommerfeldt</em></p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/vFFkGKWLdmtaZ1Rd7xwbgqqvaV4=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bdc9e2c/turbine/ny-1541185063-dh41ey4nu0-snap-image', '2018-11-03', 'Denis Slattery', 'Donald Trump'),
(24, 1, 'Indonesia Lion Air flight with 189 on board crashes into sea', 'In this May 12, 2012 file photo, a Lion Air passenger jet is parked on the tarmac at Juanda International Airport in Surabaya, Indonesia', '<div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-article-body\" data-pb-name=\"Article Body (Elements)\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fxbPiu1dbbEd7r\"> <div class=\"\"> </div> <div class=\"collection collection-cards\"> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p data-page=\"1\">JAKARTA, Indonesia — A Lion Air flight with 189 people on board crashed into the sea just minutes after taking off from Indonesia\'s capital on Monday in a blow to the country\'s aviation safety record after the lifting of bans on its airlines by the European Union and U.S.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Indonesia\'s disaster agency posted photos online of a crushed smartphone, books, bags and parts of the aircraft fuselage that had been collected by search and rescue vessels that have converged on the area.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-dfp inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"1\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-dfp\" data-pb-name=\"DFP Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fdtBwp1Lfdvj8r\"> <div class=\"pb-ad pb-ad-prod ad-300x250 hidden-desktop relative\"> <div class=\"ad-caption-text align-center uppercase\">Advertisement</div> <div id=\"news_world_225\" class=\"hidden\"> </div> </div> <script>(function(){function loadAd(){window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.services.dfpService&&window.googletag&&googletag.pubadsReady)window.services.dfpService.appendAd({id:\"news_world_225\",adType:\"cube\",slotName:\"/4011/trb.nydn/news/world\",displayMobile:true,displayDesktop:false,isOOP:false,is5x1:false,dimensionsString:\"[[300, 250]]\",sizemapString:\"\",sizemapRefresh:\"false\",refreshOnPhotoChange:false,includeInA9:true,includeInIndexExchange:false,options:{ptype:\"s\",iab:\"\",apv:\"false\",site:\"trb.nydn\",\r\nslug:\"ny-news-lion-air-lost-contact-airplane-20181028\",cid:\"109505064\",at:\"Asia,EuropeanUnion\",kw:\"Indonesia,indonesia,ban,Jakarta,airline,airport,Agency,sea,Lion,flight,board,JAKARTA,Pangkal,Pinang,National,jakarta,Sumatra,lifting,Air,Boeing,meter,Surabaya,Bali,search,plane\",tg:\"AerospaceandAviation,Disaster,AccidentandTragedy\",design:\"arc\",nopulse:true}},false,true);else setTimeout(loadAd,500)})}loadAd()})();</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Lion Air said the aircraft, on a 1-hour-and-10-minute flight to Pangkal Pinang on an island chain off Sumatra, was carrying 181 passengers, including one child and two babies, and eight crew members.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Indonesian TV broadcast pictures of a fuel slick and debris field.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"desktop-nativo mobile-yieldmo inline-ad \" data-inline-ad-count=\"2\"> <span class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_2001435\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_2001435\");if(false)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_2001435\",el:el})}});</script> </div></span> <span class=\"hidden-mobile\"><div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"f9coTz1Wfdvj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-mobile\"> <div id=\"3915\" data-nativo-id-desktop=\"1089988\" class=\"desktop-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></span> </div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The National Search and Rescue Agency said the flight ended in waters off West Java that are 30 to 35 meters (98 to 115 feet) deep.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The agency\'s chief Muhammad Syaugi told a news conference that divers are trying to locate the wreckage of the plane, which according to aviation website Flightradar24 was brand-new and delivered to Lion Air in August.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"image\" class=\"card card-pull-center card-captioned collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <figure class=\"\"> <div class=\"full-width img-container \"> <img class=\"b-lazy full-width b-loaded\" alt=\"Relatives of passengers comfort each other as they wait for news on a Lion Air plane that crashed off Java Island at Depati Amir Airport in Pangkal Pinang, Indonesia Monday.\" src=\"https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/6OEs1Xn_x-dvybyAbGw2hodAkqM=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bd692fd/turbine/ny-1540788984-7bhd3z8u4i-snap-image\"> </div> <figcaption class=\"caption-text spaced spaced-top spaced-sm flex-container-row justify-space-between \"> <div>Relatives of passengers comfort each other as they wait for news on a Lion Air plane that crashed off Java Island at Depati Amir Airport in Pangkal Pinang, Indonesia Monday. (Hadi Sutrisno / AP)</div> </figcaption> </figure> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Indonesia\'s Transport Ministry said the Boeing 737 Max 8 plane, which took off from Jakarta about 6.20 a.m., crashed just 13 minutes later. Data from aircraft tracking website FlightAware showed it had reached an altitude of only 5,200 feet (1,580 meters).</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Indonesian TV showed dozens of people waiting anxiously outside the Pangkal Pinang airport and officials bringing out plastic chairs. The transport ministry said crisis centers have been set up Pangkal Pinang\'s airport and Jakarta\'s Soekarno Hatta airport.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-nativo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"3\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix full pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-nativo\" data-pb-name=\"Nativo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"fUgU9f24gdvj8r\"> <div class=\"hidden-desktop\"> <div id=\"1240\" data-nativo-id-mobile=\"1089988\" class=\"mobile-nativo-ad trb_ar_nt\"></div> </div> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>The crash is the worst airline disaster in Indonesia since an AirAsia flight from Surabaya to Singapore plunged into the sea in December 2014, killing all 162 on board.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>A report to the Jakarta Search and Rescue Office cited the crew of a tug boat which had reported seeing a Lion Air flight falling from the sky.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"image\" class=\"card card-pull-center card-captioned collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <figure class=\"\"> <div class=\"full-width img-container \"> <img class=\"b-lazy full-width\" alt=\"Relatives of passengers comfort each other as they wait for news on a Lion Air plane that crashed off Java Island at Depati Amir Airport in Pangkal Pinang, Indonesia Monday, Oct. 29, 2018.\" data-src=\"https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/5P1YOWrmffODY-Ls1dpqG2KLDIo=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bd69348/turbine/ny-1540789059-jjdemsxxxt-snap-image\" src=\"/pb/resources/images/tinygif.gif\"> </div> <figcaption class=\"caption-text spaced spaced-top spaced-sm flex-container-row justify-space-between \"> <div>Relatives of passengers comfort each other as they wait for news on a Lion Air plane that crashed off Java Island at Depati Amir Airport in Pangkal Pinang, Indonesia Monday, Oct. 29, 2018. (AP)</div> </figcaption> </figure> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>A telegram from the National Search and Rescue Agency to the air force has requested assistance with the search.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Lion Air is one of Indonesia\'s youngest and biggest airlines, flying to dozens of domestic and international destinations.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"mobile-yieldmo inline-ad hidden-desktop\" data-inline-ad-count=\"4\"> <div class=\"wrapper clearfix col pb-feature pb-layout-item pb-f-ads-yieldmo\" data-pb-name=\"Yieldmo Ad\" data-pb-curated=\"curated\" id=\"\"> <div id=\"ym_1610965632225229372\"></div> <script>window.serviceCallbacks.push(function(){if(window.isMobile.any()&&window.services.isAdEnabled(\"yieldmo\")){var el=document.getElementById(\"ym_1610965632225229372\");if(true)window.services.lazyLoadService.addPendingObject({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el,load:function(){window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el})}});else window.services.YieldmoService.load({id:\"ym_1610965632225229372\",el:el})}});</script> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>In 2013, one of its Boeing 737-800 jets missed the runway while landing on the resort island of Bali, crashing into the sea without causing any fatalities among the 108 people on board.</p> </div></div> <div data-type=\"text\" class=\"card collection-item card-border-bottom card-border-bottom-thick card-border-bottom-dark\"> <div class=\" card-content \"> <p>Indonesian airlines were barred in 2007 were flying to Europe because of safety concerns, though several were allowed to resume services in the following decade. The ban was completely lifted in June this year. The U.S. lifted a decadelong ban in 2016.</p> <div class=\"spaced spaced-md spaced-bottom hidden-mobile\"></div> <div class=\"spaced spaced-sm spaced-bottom hidden-desktop hidden-tablet\"></div> </div></div> <ul class=\"trb_ar_rt\" data-c-typename=\"article\"> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"Asia\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/asia/\">Asia</a> </li> <li class=\"trb_ar_rt_li\"> <a class=\"trb_ar_rt_a\" title=\"European Union\" href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/tags/european-union/\">European Union</a> </li> </ul> </div> </div>', 'https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/Ctd_AdIhuvuLNLVYMz6x3ljCXnA=/1400x0/www.trbimg.com/img-5bd687b2/turbine/ny-1540786088-6z0y2n5bp1-snap-image', '2018-11-05', 'Denis Slattery', 'oneplus, oneplus 3t, test pin');

